<sentence type="quasi">先番コミ５目半　白４目半勝ち</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
<authorsData>
<sentence type="quasi">先番　九段　武宮正樹</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
<sentence type="quasi">棋聖　趙治勲</sentence>
